com.dd.plist

Class BinaryPropertyListParser

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.dd.plist.BinaryPropertyListParser

  • public class BinaryPropertyListParser
extends java.lang.Object
    Parses property lists that are in Apple's binary format. Use this class when you are sure about the format of the property list. Otherwise use the PropertyListParser class. Parsing is done by calling the static parse methods.
    Author:
    Daniel Dreibrodt
